Leslie Stefanson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leslie_Stefanson 0 Leslie Ann Stefanson (born May 10, 1971) is an American model, actress and artist. She is most known for playing the title role as Capt. Elisabeth Campbell in the film The General's Daughter. Leslie_Ann_Stefanson ( born May_10_,_1971 ) is an_American_model_,_actress_and_artist .
